00:05:55.540 --> 00:05:58.220
So imagine a PD-L1 stained

100
00:05:58.620 --> 00:06:01.800
immunohistochemistryslide in

101
00:06:02.860 --> 00:06:06.380
lung cancer. Normally, a human would

102
00:06:06.580 --> 00:06:09.520
read this and would score the PD-L1 staining intensity.

103
00:06:10.040 --> 00:06:13.960
Now you can train AI systems to do the same thing, obviously with

104
00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:17.680
potentially much better reproducibility and also

105
00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:23.480
faster turnaround, et cetera. And many of these Class A

106
00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:25.280
