107
00:06:25.640 --> 00:06:29.030
Class B would be the use of AI to indirectly

108
00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:33.020
measure existing biomarkers. For example, using

109
00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:36.980
pathology slides to make inferences

