113
00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.680
pathology slides, EGFR mutations

114
00:06:50.780 --> 00:06:54.200
in lung cancer,

115
00:06:55.140 --> 00:06:57.740
gene fusions, many other mutations, tumor

116
00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:02.680
mutational burden, and many of these can be inferred just

117
00:07:02.780 --> 00:07:06.400
from the pathology images. This is a Class B biomarker.

118
00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:10.480
There's also other works that have shown that you can predict IDH

