130
00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:49.200
AI model to predict survival and/or adjuvant

131
00:07:50.060 --> 00:07:50.380
treatment

132
00:07:52.580 --> 00:07:56.520
efficacy, et cetera. You can predict clinical endpoints directly, and this

133
00:07:56.540 --> 00:08:00.260
would be a Class C biomarker. If you're interested, if you're

